lead_paragraph: PHOENIX — Xavier Coach Sean Miller’s team exited the N.C.A.A. tournament with a blowout loss to U.C.L.A. on Saturday. But no coach in the tournament, aside from Davidson’s Bob McKillop, may have raised his market value more than Miller.
